<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sometimes-adv">sometimes <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sʌmtaɪmz/    美 /'sʌmtaɪmz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>不时；有时：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sometimes I have letters from him.
我有时会收到他的信。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The journey takes an hour, sometimes even longer.
旅程需要一个小时，有时甚至会更长。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Father <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (有时) goes to the gym with us although he dislikes going there.  （2010 湖南改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. sometimes  </p></div>